quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  20,90,Ka lheueh geupeugah dilee le Harun i Wahe kaom lon atra nyan salah Ka jifitnah dum nyan keu gata Nyang Tuhan gata cit sidroe Allah Ikot lon jinoe tathaʻat keu lon Beu tapateh lon peue nyang lon peugah
  20,91,Jikheuen treuk sabe kamoe seumah nyoe Meu goh troh keu noe Musa geulangkah Meu goh woe Musa meuseumah sabe
  20,92,Musa geukheun le aduen meutuah Hai Harun pakon han tatham jih nyan Ka taeu jih nyan sisat sileupah
  20,93,Peue gata han le tatem ikot lon Nyang peurintah lon sang-sang tabantah
  20,94,Geukheun le aduen hai aneuk ma lon Pakon janggot lon tarinthak bagah r Bek le ulee lon tamat lagee nyan Cit teumakot lon takheun lon salah Ka tapeucre bre Bani Israi Han tapadoli peue nyang lon peugah
  20,95,Kheun Musa teuma kah hai Samiri Pakon buet keuji kapeubuet dikah
  20,96,Seuot Samiri dilon ka lon eu Nyang hana gop eu lon cok treuk bagah 7 Tanoh sigeupai euncit Rasul jak Lon tiek saboh cak bak patong sudah Jikheun le napsu dilon lagee nyan
  20,97,Kheun Musa youh nyan boh jak weh dikah Lam udep donya kakheun bek teupeh Dilon kujakweh meunan kapeugah y Uroe akhirat keu kah ‘azeub that Han ek beurangpat pih na soe peuglah Ka eu Tuhankah nyang ka seumah nyan Kamoe tet jih nyan lam apui mirah Lheueh nyan kamoe tiek keudeh lam laot Keu umpeuen eungkot hanco dum bicah
  20,98,Tapi Tuhankah cit sidroe Tuhan Tan laen Tuhan meulengkan Allah Maha kuasa Tuhan Hadharat Dumpeue Neutupat ‘eleumee-Neuh luah
  20,99,Meunankeuh Kamoe meupeugah khaba Nyang dilee masa bandum meukisah Teuma keu gata pih ka Kamoe bri y Qur’an suci ziker keu Allah
  20,100,Soe nyang han tem ngui Qur'an jimat Uroe kiamat geuhon that salah í Geuhon that jime dacha jih nyang nyan
  20,101,Keukai jime nyan ngon brat sileupah Brok that awih jih uroe kiamat i
  20,102,Uroe nyan meuhat meuri soe salah € Uroe nyan geuyup ngon Sangkai Kala Ureueng meudacha muka dum mirah Kamoe peusapat sabe meudacha Keulabee muka krot sang beurintah
  20,103,Jimeus‘ah-sʻah dum sabe keudoe-droe Sang siploh uroe sagai tasinggah
  20,104,Kamoe nyang teupeue nyang dipeugah nyan i Nyang got pikiran teuma kheun bagah Tinggaiteuh sideh siuroe sagai Jinoe nyang keukai hana peue peugah